Generate the autocompletion script for agentclash for the specified shell.
See each sub-command's help for details on how to use the generated script.

Usage:
  agentclash completion [command]

Available Commands:
  bash        Generate the autocompletion script for bash
  fish        Generate the autocompletion script for fish
  powershell  Generate the autocompletion script for powershell
  zsh         Generate the autocompletion script for zsh

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for completion

Global Flags:
      --api-url string     API base URL (overrides config)
      --json               Output in JSON format
      --no-color           Disable color output
      --non-interactive    Disable interactive prompts (also honored: CI=true, AGENTCLASH_NON_INTERACTIVE=1, --json, no TTY)
  -o, --output string      Output format: table, json, yaml
  -q, --quiet              Suppress non-essential output
  -v, --verbose            Enable debug output on stderr
  -w, --workspace string   Workspace ID (overrides config)
      --yes                Skip confirmation prompts

Use "agentclash completion [command] --help" for more information about a command.
